{"tid":1317002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港真係好多劍擊好手","createTime":"2019-07-14T17:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T17:12:36.000Z","uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bdfc0c44e49b0e4bef3998670f120cd8f30bb410","tid":1317002,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:12:36.000Z","msg":"余翠怡輪椅劍擊世盃波蘭站摘銅<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】港將余翠怡（圖）昨出戰IWAS輪椅劍擊世界盃波蘭站，在女子A級花劍個人賽連退以色列隊、匈牙利隊及意大利隊劍手，躋身4強，惟其後以4：15不敵中國隊劍手，在不設季軍戰下摘銅。隊友范珮珊及吳舒婷則在16強止步，各列12及14名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkparalympic.org/data/object/2/58/79_17_WheelchairFencing.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkparalympic.org%2Fdata%2Fobject%2F2%2F58%2F79_17_WheelchairFencing.jpg&h=2ad5c97e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為香港運動員嘅強項，硬係覺得劍擊喺香港可以更普及，市民可以用類似嘅日常工具學習/練習，都幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}